//vectorstore interface have multiple implementations like PGvectorstore, simplevectorstore,  as we have the autoconfiguration spring boot is automatically going to pick up the PGvector store for us 
        vectorStore.accept(documents);
        log.info("Completed Ingesting PDF file");
    }
}

